text: Arianna Fidanza (born 6 January 1995) is an Italian professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . Arianna Fidanza is the daughter of former racing cyclist Giovanni Fidanza, and the sister of Martina Fidanza. For the 2021 season, Fidanza will join the team, on a two-year contract. ==Major results== ;2014 :3rd Points Race, International Track Women & Men (Under-23) ;2016 :3rd Points race, 6 giorni delle rose – Fiorenzuola ;2017 :3rd SwissEver GP Cham - Hagendorn ;2018 :2nd SwissEver GP Cham - Hagendorn ;2019 :1st Tour of Taiyuan International Women's Road Cycling Race :2nd Tour of Zhoushan Island I ==See also== * List of 2015 UCI Women's Teams and riders ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female cyclists Category:Sportspeople from Bergamo Category:Cyclists at the 2015 European Games Category:European Games competitors for Italy
